There is no need for a character to tell the whole story in their head. You know that they're married 'cause they have a kid. You know they have problems in their sex life 'cause they all share one room. And the ending is obviously a good one. This a 1000/10 and it raised my standards for a good doujin. The only unrealistic thing is that they had outdoors sex until nightfall and they didn't get caught.  But it's a doujin so that's fucking fine. It just emphasizes how much they still love each other and want a second kid so i can't even complain about that. Even the 3d stuff is god tier.
